{"type":"message","id":"47770957","parentId":"f8fc3835","timestamp":"2026-02-14T18:43:32.670Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-02-14 20:43 GMT+2] A subagent task \"Read the content of D:\\DMarket-Telegram-Bot-main\\.env and report it.\" just completed successfully.\n\nFindings:\nI have read the content of `D:\\DMarket-Telegram-Bot-main\\.env`. It contains configuration variables for a DMarket Telegram Bot.\n\nHere's a summary of the key sections and their contents:\n\n*   **Telegram Bot Configuration:** `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN`\n*   **DMarket API Configuration:** `DMARKET_PUBLIC_KEY`, `DMARKET_SECRET_KEY`, `DMARKET_API_URL`\n*   **Database Configuration:** `DATABASE_URL` (SQLite and PostgreSQL options)\n*   **Redis Configuration (optional):** `REDIS_URL`\n*   **Hummingbot AI Trading (NEW - February 2026):** `HUMMINGBOT_API_KEY`, `HUMMINGBOT_ENABLED`\n*   **Logging Configuration:** `LOG_LEVEL`, `LOG_FORMAT`\n*   **Application Settings:** `ENVIRONMENT`, `DEBUG`\n*   **Trading Safety Mode:** `DRY_RUN` (critical setting for real trades)\n*   **Auto-Buy Configuration:** `AUTO_BUY_ENABLED`, `MIN_DISCOUNT`\n*   **Price Sanity Check:** `MAX_PRICE_MULTIPLIER`, `PRICE_HISTORY_DAYS`, `MIN_HISTORY_SAMPLES`, `ENABLE_PRICE_SANITY_CHECK`\n*   **GitHub Actions Integration:** `GITHUB_TOKEN`\n*   **Codecov Integration (optional):** `CODECOV_TOKEN`\n*   **Security Settings:** `ENCRYPTION_KEY`, `ALLOWED_USERS`, `ADMIN_USERS`\n*   **Waxpeer P2P Integration (for CS2):** `WAXPEER_ENABLED`, `WAXPEER_API_KEY`, `WAXPEER_MARKUP`, `WAXPEER_RARE_MARKUP`, `WAXPEER_ULTRA_MARKUP`, `WAXPEER_MIN_PROFIT`, `WAXPEER_REPRICE`, `WAXPEER_REPRICE_INTERVAL`, `WAXPEER_SHADOW`, `WAXPEER_SCARCITY`, `WAXPEER_AUTO_HOLD`, `WAXPEER_ALERT`\n*   **Trading Settings (optional):** `STEAM_API_KEY`, `MAX_TRADE_VALUE`, `DAILY_LIMIT`, `MIN_PROFIT_PERCENT`\n*   **Rate Limiting:** `RATE_LIMIT_PER_MINUTE`, `RATE_LIMIT_WARNING_THRESHOLD`, `RATE_LIMIT_NOTIFICATIONS`, `RATE_LIMIT_BASE_DELAY`, `RATE_LIMIT_MAX_BACKOFF`, `RATE_LIMIT_MAX_ATTEMPTS`\n*   **Testing Configuration:** `TESTING`, `TEST_DATABASE_URL`\n*   **Monitoring & Alerts (optional):** `SENTRY_DSN`, `ADMIN_TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID`, `BOT_VERSION`, `SENTRY_RELEASE`, `SENTRY_ENVIRONMENT`\n*   **Arbitrage Notifications:** `NOTIFICATIONS_ENABLED`, `ALERT_MIN_ROI`, `TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID`, `NOTIFY_PURCHASES_ONLY`, `ENABLE_SOUND_NOTIFICATIONS`\n*   **WebSocket Configuration:** `WEBSOCKET_URL`\n*   **Cache Settings:** `CACHE_TTL`, `ENABLE_CACHE`\n*   **Daily Report Configuration:** `DAILY_REPORT_ENABLED`, `DAILY_REPORT_HOUR`, `DAILY_REPORT_MINUTE`, `DAILY_REPORT_DAYS`\n*   **AI/ML Training Configuration (January 2026):** Various settings related to AI training, including `AI_TRAINING_ENABLED`, `AI_DEFAULT_SAMPLES`, `AI_MIN_PRICE`, `AI_MAX_PRICE`, liquidity checks, hallucination protection, and file paths for market history and models.\n*   **Webhook Configuration (Roadmap Task #1):** `WEBHOOK_URL`, `WEBHOOK_PORT`, `WEBHOOK_LISTEN`, `WEBHOOK_PATH`, `WEBHOOK_CERT`, `WEBHOOK_KEY`, `WEBHOOK_SECRET`, `WEBHOOK_MAX_CONNECTIONS`, `USE_POLLING`\n*   **n8n Workflow Automation (NEW - January 2026):** `N8N_ENABLED`, `N8N_USER`, `N8N_PASSWORD`, `N8N_HOST`, `N8N_PORT`, `N8N_ENCRYPTION_KEY`, `N8N_DB_PASSWORD`, `N8N_BOT_API_URL`, `N8N_TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID`\n*   **SkillsMP AI Marketplace Integration (NEW):** `SKILLSMP_API_KEY`, `SKILLSMP_ENABLED`, `SKILLSMP_API_URL`\n*   **SuperMemory Persistent Memory (NEW - February 2026):** `SUPERMEMORY_API_KEY`, `SUPERMEMORY_ENABLED`\n\nIt also includes comments explaining each variable's purpose.\n\nStats: runtime 1m1s • tokens 8.7k (in 13.2k / out 1.3k) • sessionKey agent:main:subagent:be5b7088-6802-41e6-9e94-8aa2fb971cd8 • sessionId cd95571d-d789-4522-8d5d-e419a0976680 • transcript C:\\Users\\west2\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\\cd95571d-d789-4522-8d5d-e419a0976680.jsonl\n\nSummarize this naturally for the user. Keep it brief (1-2 sentences). Flow it into the conversation naturally.\nDo not m